body:
https://github.com/eBay/fabio/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#v134---28-oct-2016

The linux_amd64 and darwin_amd64 are known to work well. All other platforms are considered experimental. Please provide feedback.

Release v1.3 has a bug which may choose the wrong listener protocol in some situations. See #157. Please use v1.3.1 instead.

https://github.com/eBay/fabio/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#v13---9-sep-2016

Issue #128: fabio -v panics
Please add `registry.consul.service.status = passing` to your fabio.properties for now. Otherwise, the healthy services won't be picked up. Fixed in 1.2

Issue #108: Mark ApiGateway certificates as CA certs
Issue #128: fabio -v panics. Fixed in 1.2rc4
If you terminate SSL on fabio this release will not detect the SSL connection properly. Fixed in 1.1.3rc2
